(131, 321359, 'Hola Cat', 'hola-cat', 'Hola Cat is a new, fun and addictive puzzle game suitable for all ages.- Find the correct orientation of the objects to deliver and shoot the yarn ball to deliver it to your cat and make her happy!- Avoid dropping the ball on the ground as you have 3 balls for each level.- The puzzles become harder as you advance through handcrafted levels.- Various objects may make finding the correct path easier or harder for you!- We hear you! Make sure to rate Hola Cat and let us know about what you like!', '2018-12-02', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/2c9/2c91df7485da8401ae857f70e5a658db.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Sonmez Sogut', 'Sonmez Sogut', NULL, NULL),
