(143, 169262, 'Snobs like it clean !', 'snobs-like-it-clean', 'We squires work Day by Day for these snobs and how do they thank us? \nThey scream at us!\n So Gather, my Comrades!  And kill as many snobs as you can! \nMy Snob likes it clean and tidy but all this intestines pile up with all this fighting and My Snob will go crazy if there are too many. But the battlefield is the best method to get rid of him.\nSo I will tidy up and Burn them so i can kill as many Generations of this snobby familie as possible.\nWhat a coincidence the devil is right here!\nR : Restart the game (blocked)\nJ : to pickup body parts, cremate them or pickup body parts from the cupboard\nK : to buy new  furnaces or upgrades from the devi\nL : to put the body parts in the cupboard\nW, A, S, D : to move\n\nGreen : clean and tidyYellow : could be betterOrange : too muchRed : I\'m leaving now      +        =      Its Heaven coins for cremate of body parts!The devil- upgrade monster- upgrade your bag- cleans up for youThe snob (your Enemy)The servant (the Player)The Monster (our friends)\n\nPost-jam Update !\n- rearrange controls\n- ingame tutorial\n- instead of any key you have to press a button\n- for now restart is blocked \n- monster update got an downgradejust to make sure!\n\nCredits : for Music\n\"Master of the Feast\" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)\nLicensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0 Licensehttp://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/\n\"Running Fanfare\" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)\nLicensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0 Licensehttp://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/', '2018-08-13', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/820/82009a2e258bf19634783f590b530d39.jpg', NULL, 0, 'GentlemenTeaparty', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(144, 160719, 'Clean A Way', 'clean-a-way', 'Remember this game is still been worked on.The aim of the game is to clean up all the dirt on the floor before the timer runs out. You dont know where they are or how many patches are left. Its a top down view of a maze where you play as a hoover.Tip: \'Enter\' pauses the game Use W, A, S and D to move', '2015-01-09', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/69a/69a24544fb0062ffcc93a50847f94ed4.jpg', NULL, 0, 'AceGuy', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(145, 438509, 'Top Down Shooty Pow Pow Boogalo', 'top-down-shooty-pow-pow-boogalo', 'Move mouse and left click to fire, Right click changes your position to a random one (costs points) and middle mouse button opens loot box (costs points).', '2020-04-27', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/fdd/fdd7bb5702c900247523710b1dca660c.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Hobo91', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(146, 891960, 'Pow Pow Pew Pew Simulator', 'pow-pow-pew-pew-simulator', 'Pow Pow Pew Pew Simulator é um jogo que se passa no ano de 2024, onde zumbis tomaram conta do planeta terra. Seu trabalho como soldado é eliminar esses zumbis! Bom trabalho', '2022-12-07', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/744/744e4a179889b6ad1613a4545dc6361a.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Daniciti', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(147, 983166, 'Pow Vista', 'pow-vista', 'Welcome to Pow Vista, an exciting MMO originally crafted for iOS, now available on Steam!\n\r\nIn Pow Vista, you start your journey as a skateboarder living at home with your mom. Despite her warnings to avoid the skateboarders out in the world, you can\'t help but explore. Stepping outside, you\'re greeted by Ava, who hands you your first skateboard. From there, you dive into a world full of challenges and adventures, including the daunting Volcano Challenge where you must defeat a powerful lava boss.\n\r\nSkateboarding is your primary mode of travel, and as you zoom around the world, you\'ll gain XP, level up, and encounter other players in real-time. The game features a variety of skills to master, like the Fire skill for cooking and the Water skill for fishing. Rare drops and formidable enemies keep the gameplay fresh.\n\r\nTo really experience the thrill of Pow Vista, you need to dive in and start playing. Get ready to level up, meet new friends, and conquer epic challenges. Enjoy!', '2024-06-06', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/4de/4deae8f7ca2e943bd184d0c63932eda7.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Aram Audio', 'Aram Audio', NULL, NULL),
(148, 530226, 'Inkia Pow', 'inkia-pow', 'A simple platformer game that requires a player to collect peas to unlock doors. Shoot, jump, die and repeat. The game is still in beta and has more work required.', '2020-12-07', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/c76/c762cc76a1f1afa726bc8da2321a22b8.jpg', NULL, 0, 'kookoojames', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(149, 399341, 'Top Down Shooty Pow Pow', 'top-down-shooty-pow-pow', 'Play an intense 1v1 in a battle arena against your opponent! Pick up the gun closest to your character, and start shooting!\nUse left thumbstick to move and right to aim.\nRight Bumper to Shoot.\nPress X on PS4 or A on XBox controllers to swap weapons.', '2019-12-13', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/461/4613a80e2519505aed73e99d1aab2a42.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Cold Kirel', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(150, 24574, 'Fantasy Zone II', 'fantasy-zone-ii', 'Ten years have elapsed since Opa-Opa restored peace to the Fantasy Zone™. Now history is repeating itself, and the planets that make up the Fantasy Zone once again find themselves attacked by the mastermind of the Nenon planet forces. This mastermind is secretly constructing a huge fortress in the Fantasy Zone and aims to put an end to their ambitious plans. Just as he did ten years ago, Opa-Opa must do battle to save the Fantasy Zone!', '1987-10-17', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/ffa/ffac11306ffadc8e031f1124d44906d8.jpg', 81, 0, 'SEGA', 'SEGA', NULL, NULL),
(151, 362600, 'EyeToy: Kinetic', 'eyetoy-kinetic', 'EyeToy: Kinetic offers a wide variety of fitness activities that far exceeds the traditional &#39;home workout video&#39;. The EyeToy camera, with the addition of a newly developed Wide Angled Lens that attaches to the front of the camera, allows for increased levels of interactivity projecting the exerciser&#39;s image onto the television screen, enabling them to physically interact with their environments. With four areas of discipline to choose from, EyeToy: Kinetic offers a wide variety of exercises for players to choose from. Aero Motion and Combat zones help to increase the player&#39;s overall fitness level, inspired by moves and stances from activities such as Tai Kwon Do, Modern Dance, Kick Boxing, Aerobics and Karate. The Mind and Body zone focuses on breathing, concentration and flexibility, taking inspirations from Yoga and Tai Chi, leaving players feeling relaxed, yet with their body fully conditioned. The Toning zone helps the player to tone specific muscle groups utilizing slow and refined movements.', '2005-09-23', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/28b/28bf7812c487989313989f50c6f4fb97.jpg', 78, 1, 'SCEE London Studio', 'SCEA', NULL, NULL),
(152, 54441, 'Medal of Honor: European Assault', 'medal-of-honor-european-assault', 'In Medal of Honor European Assault gamers play as US Army Lieutenant William Holt, hand-picked by William &quot;Wild Bill&quot; Donovan to be the first field agent of the newly formed Office of Strategic Services -- the OSS. As Lieutenant Holt, your classified missions take place in WWII Europe and are of critical importance to the Allies. You are tasked with gathering intelligence regarding the development and deployment of the deadly Nazi Tiger Tank and more significantly, stopping the Nazi plan to develop and harness atomic energy. In the pursuit of this goal you are thrust into action in all the pivotal battles of WWII Europe, including St. Nazaire, North Africa, Stalingrad, and the Battle of the Bulge.', '2005-06-07', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/f6d/f6d58f9419611f48e997efaa7f3ab6eb.jpg', 72, 37, 'Electronic Arts Los Angeles', 'Electronic Arts', NULL, NULL),
(153, 183830, 'Boogeyman (W)', 'boogeyman-w', 'Controles:Arriba = SaltoIzq = Detenerse\nDesarrolladores:\nAnthony UrbinaMauricio Flores', '2018-08-01', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/3dd/3ddd72730904634aa0c46d46a8015afb.jpg', NULL, 0, 'TLS', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(154, 4791, 'Tactics Ogre: Let Us Cling Together', 'tactics-ogre-let-us-cling-together', 'The creators of Final Fantasy Tactics bring you the next evolution in Tactics games from Square Enix in Tactics Ogre: Let Us Cling Together! A dream team lead by Yasumi Matsuno has reunited to bring a perfect vision of their lost tale of political intrigue, conquest, and rebellion to vivid life. Experience an epic story where your choices determine the fate of the Walister Resistance.', '1995-10-06', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/36e/36ec9e6536619df636dfa2f3c5be88a3.jpg', 87, 31, 'Square Enix', 'Square Enix', NULL, NULL),
(155, 963416, 'Nickelodeon Barnyard', 'nickelodeon-barnyard', 'Bring the Barnyard movie to life! Battle the coyote invaders, tee up for a game of golf, target the bulls eye with your flying chicken and race downhill on your speedy bike. Explore a fully interactive, 3D world and prove they have what it takes to be the biggest party animal of them all.', '2006-08-01', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/770/7705cc7e84e74d89d906863f95860c2f.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Halfbrick Studios', 'THQ', NULL, NULL),
(156, 25062, 'Barnyard', 'barnyard', 'Enter the world of Nickelodeon&#39;s newest adventure and bring the Barnyard\nmovie to life. Battle the coyote invaders, tee up for a game of golf,\ntarget the bull&#39;s-eye with your flying chicken and race downhill on your\nspeedy bike. Players will be able to explore a fully interactive, 3-D\nworld and prove they have what it takes to be the biggest party animal\nof them all.\nFeatures\nAll your favorite Barnyard characters from the movie\nReplayable action-packed games based on the wild antics of Otis\nOpen-world gameplay through areas seen in the movie\nUnique controller functions - steering cars, swinging golf clubs,\nthrowing darts, shooting a tomato gun at coyotes, and more\nUp-rez&#39;d graphics including 60 fps, progressive scan, and widescreen\nsupport\nAll-new mini-games and customization options', '2006-08-01', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/b0c/b0c0e1853ec6a822aae9ec65894b58f0.jpg', 66, 46, 'Halfbrick', 'THQ', NULL, NULL),
(157, 257254, 'Our World Is Ended', 'our-world-is-ended', 'A new masterpiece of narrative visual novel storytelling. Follow Judgement 7, a team of eccentric developers working on their latest game in Augmented Reality. On a summer’s day, their AR headset let them catch a glimpse of Tokyo in ruins. Could it really be the end of the world?', '2017-11-09', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/303/303df7cd72c7963566ca10692d076d1c.jpg', 59, 4, 'Pqube', 'PQube', NULL, NULL),
(158, 122076, 'Wash Hero', 'wash-hero', 'Wash Hero!\n\nA rhythm game based on our love of the bath house in spirited away and the creatures that inhabit it!\n\nThis bath house caters to all those mystical spirits who need to unwind after a mucky day doing what spirits do. Help the staff scrub the tubs and fill their baths with the best herbal remedies for the job.\n\nClean the tub, get the right combo written on the herbal water tags, and stick to the beat! \n\n#MovieGameJam', '2018-02-11', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/96d/96d1e3c8a4c9840b9631cf9e8d138fb6.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Secretcat', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(159, 455380, 'washing cuttlefish simulator 5', 'washing-cuttlefish-simulator-5', 'washing cuttlefish simulator 5 is a simulation game developed by tyo_epic. It came out on 12-06-2020. washing cuttlefish simulator 5 is available on PC. You can purchase the game on itch.io. \n\n', '2020-06-12', NULL, NULL, 0, 'tyo_epic', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(160, 468020, 'Wash The Spiders Away!', 'wash-the-spiders-away', 'Hi! Thanks for playing Wash the Spiders Out! My Contribution to GMTK2020.\nThis is the first thing I’ve ever developed and finished solo. So, sorry that it’s a bit simple and a bit buggy.\nPremise: \nTo go along with the theme of “Out of Control” I’ve decided to make an Auto Battler in the vain of Stick War or Civilizations Wars style “strategy” games. In those style games, you can’t control your units directly, only spawn them. I’ve decided to make it even more idle.\nHow to play:\nThe units are random. The time they spawn is random. And the only direct control you have is a button you can use to get them to move forward. This button also buffs them with a random stat, which is not known to you. So, you can choose to spam the charge button for a strong frontline of units, or build up units for a massive wave. Once you run out of Units and your field is clear, the game is over. Kill as many spiders as you can.\nCredit:\nMusic:\nAggressive Bit by J-DiewYX\nhttps://j-dieswyx.newgrounds.com/', '2020-07-12', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/fd1/fd1f40e31e912bb975d38dcbe8584c17.jpg', NULL, 0, 'KindSpark', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(161, 54715, 'Power Stone 2', 'power-stone-2', 'Power Stone 2(パワーストーン 2) is a multiplayer fighting game that built on the innovative gameplay introduced by its predecessor, Power Stone. Power Stone 2 allows up to four players to choose from multiple characters and utilize items such as tables, chairs, and rocks in battle.\nPower Stone 2 originated as an arcade game, like many others on the Dreamcast. The Dreamcast served as a testing ground for successful arcade games. Power Stone 2 included some differences from the original, including new character voices, the removal of the existing combo system and a new, horizontal status bar.', '2000-08-23', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/d88/d8847a26e6fa3700b3a855cc6a553287.jpg', 87, 13, 'Capcom', 'Capcom', NULL, NULL),
(162, 24962, 'Kirby: Canvas Curse', 'kirby-canvas-curse', 'Your DS stylus has been magically infused with the power to paint! When\nKirby gets turned into a ball by an evil witch, your hand-drawn rainbow\npaths become the only way he can find power-ups and reach the gates of\neach world. Draw loops to make him speed up, make ramps to jump danger,\nand draw walls to block laser beams and cannon blasts as you explore\nseven levels packed with adventure.\nKirby: Canvas Curse delivers all of the classic copying action Kirby\nfans expect, while utilizing some of the most innovative touch-screen\ncontrols we&#39;ve seen on Nintendo DS. Don&#39;t let Kirby&#39;s pink exterior fool\nyou -- Canvas Curse is a perfectly balanced game that challenges players\nof all skill levels.', '2005-06-13', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/0fa/0fa4d2259a8e658dff0ebb4ab4ab8fc5.jpg', 86, 27, 'HAL Laboratory', 'Nintendo', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `video_games` (`id`, `rawg_id`, `name`, `slug`, `description`, `release_date`, `image_url`, `metacritic_score`, `review_count`, `developer`, `publisher`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(163, 5624, 'Mega Man Powered Up', 'mega-man-powered-up', 'Mega Man is on a quest to restore peace in the world after Dr. Wily takes control of several robots in hopes to rule the planet. Completely re-designed for the PSP® with new bosses and puzzles to master, Mega Man Powered Up is the only action platformer that lets gamers create their own levels and share with friends.', '2006-03-02', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/4c0/4c012de96402f00f7992e8be00b5a01f.jpg', 82, 8, 'Capcom U.S.A', 'Capcom', NULL, NULL),
(164, 300688, 'MegaMan Powered Up', 'megaman-powered-up', 'Mega Man Powered Up[a] is a side-scrolling platform video game developed and published by Capcom. It was released for the PlayStation Portable (PSP) handheld game console in March 2006. It is a remake of the original Mega Man game released in 1987 for the Nintendo Entertainment System (NES). Players control the eponymous star Mega Man who must stop Dr. Wily from conquering the world using eight robots called Robot Masters. Unlike the original game, players can control these eight Robot Masters under the right circumstances. Other new features include a level creator mode and a challenge mode.\nFirst revealed in 2005, Powered Up was produced by series mainstay Keiji Inafune. It was released in a bundle alongside Mega Man: Maverick Hunter X (also for PSP) and was slated for release on the PSP&#39;s PlayStation Network (PSN). It was released for the PSN service in Japan, but a US release did not occur due to technical difficulties. The game uses a chibi-style that was intended for the original game but was not possible at the time. The designers intended to keep this design faithful to the way the characters worked and looked in the original. While it received generally positive reviews, the game sold poorly, and plans for a remake of Mega Man 2 titled Mega Man Powered Up 2 fell through.', '2006-03-14', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/cb3/cb39060f1b78e868d43816bb0b2fa8a2.jpg', 82, 3, 'Capcom', 'Capcom', NULL, NULL),
(165, 27437, 'Mario Tennis: Power Tour', 'mario-tennis-power-tour', 'Players can test their backhand in this unique role-playing tennis adventure. Train hard at the Royal Tennis Academy to be a champion. Gain experience and improve your skills through lessons and tournaments, and rise to the top of the ranks. Play as Mario, Peach, Waluigi, or Donkey Kong in a slew of wild modes. Advance through the story and unlock even more characters, all with their own power moves. Beat Mario at his own game, then link up with a friend or three for even more frantic fun.', '2005-09-13', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/647/647174a1ecf75d11dcd532098a1a2349.jpg', 81, 18, 'Camelot Software Planning', 'Nintendo', NULL, NULL),
(166, 484816, 'DRAGON QUEST XI S: Echoes of an Elusive Age - Definitive Edition', 'dragon-quest-xi-s-echoes-of-an-elusive-age-definitive-edition', 'OVERVIEWDRAGON QUEST XI S is the last entry in the legendary RPG series from creator Yuji Horii, character designer Akira Toriyama and composer Koichi Sugiyama. This eleventh main entry is a completely standalone experience that features new characters, a beautifully detailed world, finely tuned turn-based combat, and an immersive story that will appeal to longtime fans and franchise newcomers alike. After its release in Japan, DRAGON QUEST XI won multiple gaming awards and received critical praise, including PlayStation’s Platinum Prize and a perfect 40/40 score from Famitsu (an influential video game publication in Japan).\nSTORY\nA young man, about to participate in his village’s coming of age ceremony, travels to a sacred stone alongside his childhood friend. After a series of unexpected events, this intrepid adventurer learns he is the reincarnation of a legendary hero from a forgotten age.\nThe young hero sets forth into an unknown world on a journey to unravel the mystery of his past… but the welcome he receives is far from warm. Upon revealing his identity to the King, the hero is branded as “The Darkspawn” and hunted by a relentless army.\nFleeing from his pursuers, the hero assembles a band of endearing adventurers who believe he is actually The Luminary reborn. The Luminary and his newfound companions embark on a quest that will take them across continents and over vast oceans as they learn of an ominous threat facing the world.KEY FEATURES\nUnravel an Epic Mystery in a Riveting Tale – You are the Luminary, the reincarnation of a hero from a forgotten age. Denigrated as a demon and pursued by a malicious monarch, you must embark on a quest to uncover the mystery of your fate and save a doomed world. Be prepared for an immersive story with twists and turns that pull you in and keep you craving more.\nAssemble a Colorful Cast of Loyal Companions – Accompanying you is an endearing band of adventurers with their own rich backstories and personalities. Famed manga artist Akira Toriyama brings the characters of DRAGON QUEST to life with his one-of-a-kind style.\nExplore a Massive, Beautiful, Living World – Excitement lurks around every corner, observe NPC’s attend to their daily schedules, monsters change behaviors to fit their environments, and access new areas, by foot, on horseback or with the use of monstrous vehicles.\nEngage in Classic Turn-based Battles with a Modern Twist – DRAGON QUEST XI features mechanics simple enough for beginners, but with enough depth to satisfy hardcore fans. As your adventure continues, learn incredible new abilities to take down even the most fearsome foe with your powerful allies.\nHave Some Fun &amp; Save the World – Tons of side-quests and addicting mini-games awaits you for enough content to keep you playing for well over 100 hours. You will face insurmountable odds and an evil force of unimaginable power… but while the stakes are high, there are many fun distractions to find if you know where to look.\nChallenge Yourself with the Draconian Quest - Available when you start a new game, these options allow you to craft you own customized difficulty with different settings and provide a greater challenge.', '2019-09-27', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/7af/7afce909f5f8510015209451984b683e.jpg', 91, 42, 'Square Enix', 'Square Enix', NULL, NULL),
(167, 32797, 'No One Lives Forever 2: A Spy in H.A.R.M.\'s Way', 'no-one-lives-forever-2-a-spy-in-harms-way', 'Cate Archer, the fearless and fashionable secret agent, returns to save the world from H.A.R.M. Armed with an assortment of superspy weaponry and gadgets, Cate must explore exotic locales, avoid devious traps, and defeat deadly agents to foil a Soviet project. As Cate, it&#39;s up to you to avert a nuclear holocaust through 40 single-player missions. No One Lives Forever 2 also features a multiplayer mode that lets you play cooperatively with your friend over the Internet.', '2002-10-01', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/24a/24a7490f304e74d503bd461bc23b37a2.jpg', 91, 111, 'Monolith Productions', 'Sierra Entertainment', NULL, NULL),
(168, 13633, 'Sid Meier\'s Civilization V', 'sid-meiers-civilization-v', 'Real-time strategy genre has always been about domination over your opponent, and Civilization in general expanded on the concept. Civilization 5 allows players to pick one of the 43 civilizations available in, including DLCs and the expansions. After that players in single player or multiplayer games will place their first cities, which will act as capital, and begin the race. In order to win, players will have to meet one of the following conditions:\n- defeating every other existing nation through combat to get Domination Victory;\n- building and launching a spaceship to get Science victory; \n- completing the Utopia project by filling out 5 trees of social policies, to get Social Victory;\n- winning a vote after establishing the  United Nations, to get the Diplomatic victory;\n- getting the highest score at the end of the time period, if no other win condition was reached, to get Time Victory.\nEvery civilization is represented by one of the most influential historical figures and voiced in the language of that nation. Easy to pick up game mechanics of research, foraging, and building, allow the player to immerse themselves into the game atmosphere of continuous development.', '2010-09-21', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/55e/55ee6432ac2bf224610fa17e4c652107.jpg', 90, 2004, 'Aspyr Media', '2K Games', NULL, NULL),
(169, 326238, 'Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020', 'microsoft-flight-simulator-2020', 'Microsoft Flight Simulator is the next generation of one of the most beloved simulation franchises. From light planes to wide-body jets, fly highly detailed and stunning aircraft in an incredibly realistic world. Create your flight plan and fly anywhere on the planet. Enjoy flying day or night and face realistic, challenging weather conditions.', '2020-08-18', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/89c/89ceadfd42109aa0d80e9c5dbc86f277.jpg', 90, 271, 'Asobo Studio', 'Microsoft Studios', NULL, NULL),
(170, 35655, 'ToCA Race Driver 2: Ultimate Racing Simulator', 'toca-race-driver-2-ultimate-racing-simulator', 'ToCA Race Driver 2: The Ultimate Racing Simulator is a massive step forward from Race Driver. It offers a great selection of aspirational cars to be driven through 31 championships that cover a huge variety of motor racing styles. ToCA Race Driver 2 contains the most diverse range of motorsports (including Open Wheel Grand Prix, Super Truck racing, Stockcar Oval Racing, Rally, Rallycross, Ice-Racing, Formula Ford, Classic Racing, Convertible Racing, Street Racing, GT Racing and Performance Cars) ever seen in a racing game, including the DTM and V8 Supercars licenses.', '2004-04-15', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/316/3161ed63070261ab7fb343c2ba90b71a.jpg', 82, 8, 'Codemasters', 'Codemasters', NULL, NULL),
(171, 926885, 'PowerWash Simulator Game 2022', 'powerwash-simulator-game-2022', 'Wash the Dirty of your House and Relax your mind, clean the every speck of dirt and pollution from everywhere you fell. Caught up the points after doing tasks.Features:Multiple Water guns to cleanHigh Quality GraphicsCleaning sound effectsPowerwashing man', '2023-02-01', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/e9b/e9bda1ad61e0258b027bb46bc532a5e5_Uwh9dzs.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Zaima Mukhtar', 'Zaima Mukhtar', NULL, NULL),
(172, 968141, 'PowerWash Adventure', 'powerwash-adventure', 'Immerse yourself in the thrilling experience of power washingIn PowerWash Adventure, you can literally get your hands on the exhilarating feeling of rinsing and relieving pressure. The operation of the game is super simple: use the high-pressure water gun to flush items to clean. As a casual and stress relieving rinsing simulation game, you can start and end it at any time without gameplay pressure. We also offer a variety of immersive themes: weightless space, cleaning workshop, and a variety of animals on the prairie!Offers a variety of scenarios and charactersYou\'re a city cleaner protecting the the environment, you\'re an astronaut in space rinsing a space station, or you can be the archaeologist rinsing a statue of Anubis in the Sahara Desert. Richly themed levels and expansion DLCs allow you to experience the multiverse!No pressure, just flush!The game\'s interactive mechanism is as simple as picking up a high-pressure water gun and rinsing the items in the scene to make them clean. Players can configure different nozzles for the water gun to feel the different spraying feeling and enjoy the immersive rinsing process. You can start and finish the game at any time, so you won\'t feel the game stress. We also provide a handy little helper to help you easily find hidden stains and unlock 100% of the rinsing progress, so say goodbye to compulsive disorder!', '2023-10-19', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/731/7311427d5119fa7e382c325101fb6302.jpg', NULL, 0, 'Grass Digital Technology', 'Grass Digital Technology', NULL, NULL),
(173, 581104, 'PowerWash Simulator', 'powerwash-simulator', 'POWERWASH SIMULATORHunt down dirt wherever it’s hiding, respond to calls from across the world, build your own power-washing business and unlock new tools, upgrades and more – all with the soothing satisfaction of power-washing to a sparkling finish!RELEASE THE PRESSUREAbsorb the relaxing atmosphere and stress-free pace as you strip dirt from patios and pavements, vehicles and public parks. Stress gets to us all, so here you can channel all your tension and wash your worries down the drain!CLEANING WITH MEANINGDo you like cleaning in circles or stripes? Are you methodical or chaotic? Here you are free to express yourself by cleaning the way you want.RELAX TO THE MAXIn the campaign mode there&#39;s no right or wrong; no time pressure or final score. Just you and the tools you need to soak away your stress with relaxation and satisfaction. We truly believe this is the most satisfying and relaxing game you’ll ever play!OH, YOU’VE GOT SKILLS TOO?Of course, if you think you’ve got what it takes to be the best in the business, there are challenge modes and a leaderboard with multiplayer coming too, but that is only for people who seek it.EXERCISE YOUR CREATIVITY(Coming during Early Access)\nYour nozzles are your brushes, the neighbourhood is your personal canvas. Unleash your creative instinct and transform ordinary dirt into exceptional artwork. Share your artwork and spread the relaxing power of power-washing - take photos, share your techniques and showcase your power-washing prowess and mud-caked masterpieces!MULTIPLAYER WASH TEAMS(Coming during Early Access)\nInvite a friend to join you on career jobs, or create multiplayer hangouts for up to six friends. Here you’ll be able to chat whilst washing larger spaces, helping to turn your neighbourhood into the brightest place on Earth!\nRelease the pressure, with PowerWash Simulator!', '2022-07-14', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/659/65959a07c4e6dc7a9034993bbb3ba232.jpg', NULL, 153, 'FuturLab', 'FuturLab', NULL, NULL),
(174, 441603, 'Fro Fro\'s Adventures (Bitter Jam)', 'fro-fros-adventures-bitter-jam', '-----------------------------------\nGame:\nFro Fro is an Arctic rabbit. She  finds herself dashing around the universe in search of one thing: green orbs. Why? She is a rabbit... Rabbits love green orbs.  \n-----------------------------------\nControls:\nWASD or Arrow Keys - Movement\nSPACE - Charge Dash\nWASD or Arrow Keys - Dash (When charged)\nESC - Close Game\nVisuals:\nQ - Remove TV effect\n-----------------------------------\nGame Jam:\nBITTER JAM:\nBitter Jam is a 60 hour long game jam running from May 1st, 2020 to May 4th. All games submitted must only use the tilesheet provided to jammers at the start of the jam.\nThe Tilesheet:\n\n\n\n-----------------------------------', '2020-05-04', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/eea/eeaa041dd560d16cece3bd27be0d88a0.jpg', NULL, 1, 'UEG Productions', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(175, 49332, 'FROST - A dream odyssey', 'frost-a-dream-odyssey', 'Draw paths to guide the flocking spirits to their home planets. Watch countless beautiful creatures emerge from light, bring balance to a world in constant motion, and unravel its mysteries. \nFor the first time in your pocket:\n•   Dancing Stardust\n•   Frantic Swarms\n•   … and Neutrino Flowers\nIn a breathtaking tale about attraction, interaction, and transformation.\nAlso starring:\n•   Particle Hunters\n•   Glowing Baitballs\n•   Firecracker Bouquets\n•   Living Walls\n•   Fountains of Light\n•   Supergravity Shepherds\n•   … and many more!\n Please note \nIn FROST, you can interact with swarms and flocks consisting of thousands of individual agents. To make this possible, the game utilizes the graphics technology Metal to the fullest and is therefore available only on the App Store.', '2017-10-16', 'https://media.rawg.io/media/games/112/112a5e5cdb6e045c7ff74f0938feafe1.jpg', 89, 3, 'Broken Rules', 'kunabi brother', NULL, NULL),
